org.pwr.odwa.server.metadata
Class Hierarchy

java.lang.Object
  org.pwr.odwa.server.metadata.Meta
      org.pwr.odwa.server.metadata.Hierarchy

 class Hierarchy
extends Meta

Stores internal information of a hierarchy. This class is an image of 'hierarchy' tag from metadata XML, giving a complete information set about a single hierarchy in a data warehouse project for the given dimension.

The information includes:

  • default - UID of the default level in this hierarchy
  • dimension - UID of the dimension this hierarchy belongs to
  • levels - an array of levels which belong this hierarchy

This component extends Meta class inheriting basic meta element properties from it (unique ID, name and description).
